        ]
      },
      "date": "2018-01-24 06:54:37.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests uploaded by Trevis Autotest from trevis-25vm6 for review-dne-part-3 received by maloo, run on el7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/17bb1b50-383a-483d-82ae-381197b924ea). Ran 1 tests.  1 tests failed: node-provisioning-1.",
