        "subject": "LU-9727 tests: adjust module load ordering",
        "message": "LU-9727 tests: adjust module load ordering\n\nIn test-framework::load_modules_local(), change the order in which\nmodules are loaded, by inverting mdd and mdt.\nThis is necessary to load mdt module before mdd because mdd module\nuses mdt_get_client_nid() exported by the mdt module.\n\nSigned-off-by: Sebastien Buisson <sbuisson@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I6e71a25bd53de4f523feb3a5dd92fbf27cd70028\n"
      },
